报告说球场亏损12.2万美元，但根据协议，每年的运营费用达到30万美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bronx bogey: Trump's city golf course loses money|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/ny-golf-trump-bronx-20190730-jsre6rqwazclflp2p5pkxrlh7e-story.html|accessdate=2019-08-31|author=Greene|date=2019-07-29|first=Leonard|work=Daily News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831231207/https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/ny-golf-trump-bronx-20190730-jsre6rqwazclflp2p5pkxrlh7e-story.html|archive-date=2019-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>

