== 盾形纹章 ==
特朗普在他的企业中使用了许多[[徽章|徽章]]风格的标志。{{Le|约瑟夫·E·戴维斯|Joseph E. Davies}}是美国社会名流{{Le|玛荷丽·梅莉薇德·波斯特|Marjorie Merriweet Post}}的第三任丈夫，也是一位[[威爾斯|威尔士]]出身的美国外交官，1939年英国当局授予他盾形纹章，上有用[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]写成的[[座右铭|座右铭]]{{Lang|la|Integritas}}，意为“[[誠信|诚信]]”。1985年，特朗普购买了梅莉薇德·波斯特建造的[[海湖庄园|海湖庄园]]后，特朗普集团开始在全国各地的特朗普高尔夫球场和庄园使用戴维斯的纹章。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Hakim|first=Danny|title=The Coat of Arms Said 'Integrity'. Now It Says 'Trump'.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/28/business/trump-coat-of-arms.html|accessdate=2018-02-14|work=The New York Times|date=2017-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180305223936/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/28/business/trump-coat-of-arms.html|archive-date=2018-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>它还在[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]被注册。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trademark of Trump crest|url=https://trademarks.justia.com/759/39/trump-75939343.html|accessdate=2018-02-15|work=Justia trademarks|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216085051/https://trademarks.justia.com/759/39/trump-75939343.html|archive-date=2018-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年，特朗普试图在他新开设的[[海湖庄园|海湖庄园]]启用这一美国标志，但{{Le|苏格兰纹章学|Scottish heraldry}}最高权威{{Le|皇家纹章大臣|Lord Lyon King of Arms}}警告称，[[苏格兰议会|苏格兰议会]]自1672年起的一项法案，禁止人们使用未注册的纹章。2012年1月，在该高尔夫球场落成典礼后不久，特朗普展示了2011年皇家纹章大臣授予“特朗普国际高尔夫俱乐部苏格兰有限公司”（{{Lang|en|The Trump International Golf Club Scotland Ltd}}）的新徽章（如下图）。<ref name="deadline">{{Cite news|author=Guest|title=Donald Trump awarded Scottish coat of arms after four-year battle|url=http://www.deadlinenews.co.uk/2012/01/17/donald-trump-at-last-awarded-the-scottish-coat-of-arms/|accessdate=2018-02-14|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2012-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214200437/http://www.deadlinenews.co.uk/2012/01/17/donald-trump-at-last-awarded-the-scottish-coat-of-arms/|archive-date=2018-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Trump International Golf Club Scotland Ltd was granted arms in 2011, replacing an assumed design they had previously used.|url=https://twitter.com/LyonCourt/status/798120353948049408|date=2016-11-14|last1=Court of the Lord Lyon|first1=[https://twitter.com/LyonCourt @LyonCourt]|website=Twitter|access-date=2018-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808060505/https://twitter.com/LyonCourt/status/798120353948049408|archive-date=2019-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

从2014年开始，特朗普在爱尔兰的{{Le|爱尔兰特朗普国际高尔夫球场和酒店|Trump International Golf Links and Hotel Ireland}}使用了同一个标志，这个高尔夫度假村是他收购了{{Le|Doonbeg|Doonbeg}}高尔夫俱乐部后建造的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump confirms Doonbeg buy – rebranded "Trump International Golf Links, Ireland"|url=http://www.irishgolfdesk.com/news-files/2014/2/11/trump-confirms-doonbeg-buy-rebranded-trump-international-golf-links-ireland|accessdate=2016-11-19|work=irishgolfdesk.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119120809/http://www.irishgolfdesk.com/news-files/2014/2/11/trump-confirms-doonbeg-buy-rebranded-trump-international-golf-links-ireland|archive-date=2016-11-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=About the Course – Trump International Golf Club 2016 – Doonbeg|url=http://www.trumpgolfireland.com/Default.aspx?p=dynamicmodule&pageid=100035&ssid=100052&vnf=1|accessdate=2016-11-19|work=trumpgolfireland.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119182040/http://www.trumpgolfireland.com/Default.aspx?p=dynamicmodule&pageid=100035&ssid=100052&vnf=1|archive-date=2016-11-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>战斗口号
