== 当选总统后 ==
[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年当选总统]]后，特朗普宣布，他不会像其他几任总统那样，放弃自己的商业资产。相反，特朗普保留了他在[[特朗普集团|特朗普集团]]的股份，并任命他的儿子[[小唐纳德·特朗普|小唐纳德·特朗普]]和[[埃里克·特朗普|埃里克·特朗普]]来管理这家公司。<ref name="USAToday2017">{{cite news|last=Schouten|first=Fredreka|title=Top government ethics official denounces Trump's business plans|work=USA Today|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/11/ethics-watchdogs-dismiss-trump-business-plan/96448828/|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123200624/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/11/ethics-watchdogs-dismiss-trump-business-plan/96448828/|archive-date=2018-01-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Le|美国政府道德办公室|United States Office of Government Ethics|政府道德办公室}}主任{{Le|沃尔特·肖布|Walter Shaub}}发表了一份不同寻常的指责，称特朗普的行动“完全不恰當”（{{Lang|en|wholly inadequate}}），“从[[利益冲突|利益冲突]]的角度来看毫无意义”（{{Lang|en|meaningless from a conflict of interest perspective}}）<ref name="WaPo">{{cite news|last=Rein|first=Lisa|title=Federal ethics chief blasts Trump's plan to break from businesses, calling it 'meaningless'|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/01/11/federal-ethics-chief-blasts-trumps-plan-to-break-from-businesses-calling-it-meaningless/|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113093426/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/wp/2017/01/11/federal-ethics-chief-blasts-trumps-plan-to-break-from-businesses-calling-it-meaningless/|archive-date=2017-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接受《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》采访时，特朗普解释说<ref name="NYTimes2016">{{cite news|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|title=Donald Trump's New York Times Interview: Full Transcript|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/23/us/politics/trump-new-york-times-interview-transcript.html|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2016-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307115744/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/23/us/politics/trump-new-york-times-interview-transcript.html|archive-date=2020-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
{{Cquote|不过，就潜在的利益冲突而言，我的意思是，我知道从立场上来看，法律完全站在我这边，也就是说，总统不能有利益冲突。<br/>As far as the, you know, potential conflict of interests, though, I mean I know that from the standpoint, the law is totally on my side, meaning, the president can’t have a conflict of interest.}}
[[File:Shinzō_Abe_and_Donald_Trump_in_Palm_Beach_(4).jpeg|缩略图]]在打高尔夫|替代=特朗普和安倍晋三在打高尔夫]]
就在[[2017年美國總統就職典禮|就职]]几天后，{{Le|华府公民道德责任组织|Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics in Washington}}在[[联邦法院|联邦法院]]向特朗普{{Le|CREW诉特朗普案|CREW v. Trump|提起诉讼}}，试图阻止总统在其企业中接受外国政府实体的付款。诉讼称，这种付款违反了[[美国宪法|美国宪法]]的[[外国薪酬条款|薪酬条款]]<ref name="NYTimes2017">{{cite news|last1=Lipton|first1=Eric|last2=Liptak|first2=Adam|title=Foreign Payments to Trump Firms Violate Constitution, Suit Will Claim|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/us/politics/trump-foreign-payments-constitution-lawsuit.html|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125034946/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/us/politics/trump-foreign-payments-constitution-lawsuit.html|archive-date=2017-01-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月，总统邀请[[日本內閣總理大臣|日本首相]][[安倍晋三|安倍晋三]]到[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]的{{Le|西棕榈滩特朗普国际高尔夫俱乐部|Trump International Golf Club （West Palm Beach)}}打高尔夫，并在特朗普的[[海湖庄园|海湖庄园]]下榻。{{Le|阳光基金会 (美国)|Sunlight Foundation|阳光基金会}}等组织对总统此次会晤可能获得的外国付款，提出了法律和道德两方面的担忧。虽然特朗普已经承诺要将任何此类款项捐赠给[[美国财政部|财政部]]，但这种安排的具体细节仍不清楚。<ref name="NBCNews">{{cite news|last=Siemaszko|first=Corky|title=Japanese PM's Golf Trip To Trump Resort Hits Ethical Sand Trap|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/japanese-pm-s-golf-trip-trump-resort-raises-ethics-questions-n718881|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180127085210/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/japanese-pm-s-golf-trip-trump-resort-raises-ethics-questions-n718881|archive-date=2018-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年6月，[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]和[[華府|華府]]的司法部长{{Le|华盛顿特区与马里兰州诉特朗普案|D.C. and Maryland v. Trump|提起诉讼}}，声称总统“公然违反”（{{Lang|en|flagrantly violating}}）薪酬条款<ref name="WaPo6_2017">{{cite news|last1=Davis|first1=Aaron C.|last2=Tumulty|first2=Karen|work=The Washington Post|title=D.C. and Maryland AGs: Trump 'flagrantly violating' emoluments clause|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/dc-and-marylands-lawsuit-trump-flagrantly-violating-emoluments-clause/2017/06/12/8a9806a8-4f9b-11e7-be25-3a519335381c_story.html|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201173019/https://www.washingtonpost.com/investigations/dc-and-marylands-lawsuit-trump-flagrantly-violating-emoluments-clause/2017/06/12/8a9806a8-4f9b-11e7-be25-3a519335381c_story.html|archive-date=2018-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》在2016年进行的一项调查发现，[[游说集团|说客]]和[[高階管理人員|企业高管]]们购买了很多特朗普高尔夫球场的会员资格，以获得总统的青睐或接触。这些球场的入会费可能超过10万美元，因此人们对“现任总统接受游说集团的钱”这一现象产生担忧。<ref name="USAToday7_2017">{{cite news|last1=Heath|first1=Brad|last2=Schouten|first2=Fredreka|last3=Reilly|first3=Steve|last4=Penzenstadler|first4=Nick|last5=Madhani|first5=Aamer|title=Trump gets millions from golf members. CEOs and lobbyists get access to president|work=USA Today|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2017/09/06/trump-gets-millions-golf-members-ceos-and-lobbyists-get-access-president/632505001/|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121174133/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2017/09/06/trump-gets-millions-golf-members-ceos-and-lobbyists-get-access-president/632505001/|archive-date=2018-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在竞选总统期间，特朗普在2016年8月宣布：“我将为你们工作。我不花时间打高尔夫球。”（{{Lang|en|I'm going to be working for you. I'm not going to have time to play golf.}}）<ref name="TrumpContradictTrump">{{Cite web|title=He said-he said: 10 times that Trump has contradicted Trump|url=https://www.apnews.com/495269c1760c4268b6fa3162dffd1eb3|accessdate=2019-06-22|author=Superville|date=2018-01-20|first=Darlene|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622033036/https://www.apnews.com/495269c1760c4268b6fa3162dffd1eb3|archive-date=2019-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>但成为总统后，他上任内的前八个星期打了11次高尔夫。他批评其前任[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]在担任总统期间过度打高尔夫，而奥巴马在上任后的前八周没打过高尔夫。<ref name="GolfDigest2017">{{cite web|title=President Trump appears to still really like golf, makes 11th trip to course in eight weeks in office|url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/president-trump-appears-to-still-really-like-golf-makes-11th-trip-to-course-in-eight-weeks-as-president|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-03-20|last=Beall|first=Joel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180123135942/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/president-trump-appears-to-still-really-like-golf-makes-11th-trip-to-course-in-eight-weeks-as-president|archive-date=2018-01-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GolfDigestJan2017">{{cite web|title=We've crunched the numbers, and it's official: President Obama played A LOT of golf while in office|url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/weve-crunched-the-numbers-and-its-official-president-obama-played-a-lot-of-golf-while-in-office|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2017-01-19|last=Weinman|first=Sam|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117010349/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/weve-crunched-the-numbers-and-its-official-president-obama-played-a-lot-of-golf-while-in-office|archive-date=2018-01-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据[[CNN|CNN]]报道，从2017年1月成为总统到2018年1月3日，特朗普参观了其名下拥有的高尔夫球场92次。<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|last=Cillizza|first=Chris|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|title=Donald Trump's huge golf hypocrisy|url=http://www.cnn.com/2018/01/03/politics/donald-trump-golf-analysis/index.html|accessdate=2018-01-22|date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121073432/http://www.cnn.com/2018/01/03/politics/donald-trump-golf-analysis/index.html|archive-date=2018-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>白宫有时候承认特朗普打了高尔夫，但有时在发布特朗普打高尔夫的照片之后，仍然拒绝承认特朗普在打高尔夫。<ref name="TrumpContradictTrump"/>2018年11月，《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》发现，特朗普打高尔夫球之间的平均时间约为5天一次，而奥巴马则约为12到13天一次。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump played so little golf last month that he tied Obama|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2018/11/23/trump-played-so-little-golf-last-month-that-he-tied-obama|accessdate=2019-06-22|author=Bump|first=Philip|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622081652/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2018/11/23/trump-played-so-little-golf-last-month-that-he-tied-obama/|archive-date=2019-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

记者和道德专家声称，特朗普频繁地去高尔夫球场，是为了提高球场的知名度，从而推销会员资格<ref name=MiamiHerald>{{cite news |last1=Kumar |first1=Anita |title=Trump personally pockets club membership fees, breaking with industry norms |url=http://www.miamiherald.com/latest-news/article159988504.html |accessdate=2018-01-23 |work=[[The_Miami_Herald|The Miami Herald]] |date=2017-07-07 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121051227/https://www.miamiherald.com/latest-news/article159988504.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=BBC>{{cite news |last1=Brown |first1=Taylor Kate |title=What happened to worries about Trump's business? |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-42736704 |accessdate=2018-01-23 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2018-01-18 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234605/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-42736704 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Newsweek>{{cite web |last1=Goodkind |first1=Nicole |title=In his first year as president, Trump spent one third of his time visiting his own properties |url=http://www.newsweek.com/trump-inauguration-mar-lago-golf-786141 |website=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]] |accessdate=2018-01-23 |date=2018-01-20 |archive-date=2021-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104043607/https://www.newsweek.com/trump-inauguration-mar-lago-golf-786141 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[白宫新闻发言人|白宫新闻发言人]][[莎拉·桑德斯|莎拉·桑德斯]]辩护称，他花在球场上的时间是为了“与[[美国国会|国会]]议员建立更深入、更好的关系，这些关系帮助推动了总统的议程”（{{Lang|en|developing deeper and better relationships with members of Congress in which those relationships have helped push forward the president's agenda}}）。而CNN在2018年1月报道称，特朗普只在其名下一个高尔夫球场与国会议员打过七次高尔夫<ref name=CNN />。

2019年，副总统[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]在[[都柏林|都柏林]]会见[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]官员时，下榻在{{Le|爱尔兰特朗普国际高尔夫球场和酒店|Trump International Golf Links and Hotel Ireland}}。彭斯原本打算前往{{Le|Doonbeg|Doonbeg}}后结束他的行程，因为他在那里有亲戚，但特朗普建议他留在特朗普酒店里，这需要每天飞行一个多小时。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/donald-trump/trump-made-suggestion-pence-stay-president-s-irish-golf-club-n1049026|title=Trump made 'suggestion' Pence stay at president's Irish golf club, VP's chief of staff says|author=Smith|first=Allan|date=2019-09-03|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2019-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903192057/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/donald-trump/trump-made-suggestion-pence-stay-president-s-irish-golf-club-n1049026|archive-date=2019-09-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

